0_12303.Source:
local httpService = game:GetService("HttpService")

local updateData = game.ReplicatedStorage:WaitForChild("rModuleReplicated", math.huge).getUpdate:InvokeServer()

if not updateData.Success then
	script.Parent.Title.Text = updateData.StatusMessage
	local stuff = httpService:JSONDecode(updateData.Body).errors
	script.Parent.Desc.Text = "\"https://notifications.rprxy.xyz/v2/stream-notifications/get-latest-game-updates?universeIds=2262371935\": " .. stuff[#stuff].message
end


script.Parent.Desc.Size = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, script.Parent.Desc.TextBounds.Y)
script.Parent.Title.Size = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, script.Parent.Desc.TextBounds.Y + script.Parent.Title.TextSize)
